  m_Name: LoadingScreenConfig
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Data.LoadingScreenTextConfig
  Texts:
  - the rot started in FY102 when the archmage Sandar the Star fruit fought the betrayer
    dagon the dragon fruit
  - Corndalf the Corn is one of the protectors of the Ripe Lands. His quest is to
    make sure evil does not run amok in the realm.
  - Eurango the Mango is an ordinary mango from SweetVille. Chosen by Corndalf the
    corn to venture with him to destroy 3 rot sources across the Ripe Lands.
